### API Gestor de Historias de Usuario
### Base URL: http://127.0.0.1:8000

### ==========================================
### SPRINTS
### ==========================================

### Listar sprints
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/sprints

### Ver sprint
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/sprints/1

### Crear sprint
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/sprints
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "nombre": "Sprint 1",
    "fecha_inicio": "2026-05-01",
    "fecha_fin": "2026-05-15"
}

### Editar sprint
PUT http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/sprints/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "nombre": "Sprint 1 Actualizado",
    "fecha_inicio": "2026-05-01",
    "fecha_fin": "2026-05-20"
}

### Eliminar sprint
DELETE http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/sprints/1

### ==========================================
### HISTORIAS
### ==========================================

### Listar historias
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/historias

### Crear historia
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/historias
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "titulo": "Como usuario quiero login",
    "descripcion": "Sistema de autenticación",
    "responsable": "Juan Pérez",
    "estado": "nueva",
    "puntos": 5,
    "fecha_creacion": "2026-05-10",
    "sprint_id": 1
}

### Editar historia
PUT http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/historias/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "titulo": "Como usuario quiero login con Google",
    "estado": "activa",
    "puntos": 8
}

### Eliminar historia
DELETE http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/historias/1

### Historias por sprint
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/sprints/1/historias

### ==========================================
### INFORMES
### ==========================================

### Informe por sprint
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/informes/sprints

### Informe por responsable
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/informes/responsables